'''伊莉莎白·泰瑞絲·瑪麗·海倫妮'''（{{lang-fr|'''Elisabeth Thérèse Marie Hélène'''}}, {{bd|2001年|10月25日||}}）是[[比利时君主列表|比利時國王]][[菲利普_(比利时国王)|菲利普]]同[[瑪蒂爾德_(比利時王后)|瑪蒂爾德王后]]所生的長女，也是[[比利时王位继承|比利時王位第一順位繼承人]]，現任[[布拉班特公爵|布拉班特女公爵]]，亦是比利时自1830年独立以来第一位女王储。

== 教育和军事训练 ==
2018年8月，伊莉莎白前往[[英国|英国]][[威尔士|威尔士]]的[[大西洋書院|大西洋書院]]开始两年的[[国际文凭组织|IB]][[高中|高中]]课程。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Off to College! Princess Elisabeth of Belgium Gets Kisses from Siblings as She Leaves for School|url=https://people.com/royals/princess-elisabeth-belgium-heads-off-college/|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=PEOPLE.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211204028/https://people.com/royals/princess-elisabeth-belgium-heads-off-college/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在2020年5月毕业。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Elisabeth of Belgium enrolls at Brussels' Military Academy|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-8340597/Elisabeth-Belgium-studied-Wales-enrolls-Brussels-Military-Academy.html|accessdate=2021-04-10|date=2020-05-20|last=Toureille|first=Claire|work=Mail Online|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528080723/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-8340597/Elisabeth-Belgium-studied-Wales-enrolls-Brussels-Military-Academy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，她在{{link-en|比利时皇家军事学院|Royal Military Academy (Belgium)}}完成四星期的军事训练。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Belgium's Princess Elisabeth Completes Military Initiation Training|url=https://www.forces.net/news/belgiums-princess-elisabeth-completes-military-initiation-training|accessdate=2021-04-10|last=at 3:46pm|first=29th September 2020|work=Forces Network|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105101626/https://www.forces.net/news/belgiums-princess-elisabeth-completes-military-initiation-training|dead-url=no}}</ref>

